<HL>
   BTR Has Sold Its 1.7% Stake in Norton
   In Market in Wake of Saint-Gobain Offer
   ----
   By David Stipp
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/27/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A7C
</SO>
<CO>
   NRT U.BTR F.STG
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
